## Log locations

- **BepInEx stream**: `<STATIONEERS_INSTALL>/BepInEx/LogOutput.log`, append-only during the current game session. Cleared on game restart.
- **Diagnostic-style checks**: `grep "<ModGuidOrName>" LogOutput.log | tail -30` after a repro run to find plugin-specific entries.
- **Unity Player log** (rare): `%LOCALAPPDATA%\..\LocalLow\Rocketstar Games\Stationeers\Player.log`, where native crashes usually land.

