## Test / verification workflow

1. Build Release.
2. Copy `<ModName>.dll` (and `About/About.xml` when changed) into the deploy folder.
3. If a config-default changed, delete the BepInEx config file (see above).
4. Restart Stationeers.
5. Watch `LogOutput.log` for the mod's `[Info]` startup lines and any `[Warning]` / `[Error]` / `[Fatal]` entries.
6. Run whatever in-game repro steps the test requires.
7. Grep the log for the mod name + tail recent lines.
